  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p>Wizard Coder is a code generation model based on <a href=\"https://ollama.ai/library/codellama\" rel=\"nofollow\">Code Llama</a>.</p>\n\n<h2>Versions</h2>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Tag</th>\n<th>Date</th>\n<th>Notes</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>33b</code></td>\n<td>01/042024</td>\n<td>A new 33B model trained from <a href=\"https://ollama.ai/library/deepseek-coder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deepseek Coder</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><code>python</code></td>\n<td>09/7/2023</td>\n<td>Initial release in 7B, 13B and 34B sizes based on <a href=\"https://ollama.ai/library/codellama/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Code Llama</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/WizardLM/WizardCoder-33B-V1.1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2306.08568\" rel=\"nofollow\">WizardCoder: Empowering Code Large Language Models with Evol-Instruct</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
